OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1780304989
OL,3,CZookeepers step in to hand-rear
OL,4,Cnewborn aardvark 'Womble'
OL,6,FVictoria Grimes has been speaking to
OL,7,FSmall Mammals Keeper Sophie Tyson at
OL,8,FChester Zoo
OL,10,FZookeepers at Chester Zoo have stepped
OL,11,Fin to help raise a rare newborn
OL,12,Faardvark, bottle-feeding the tiny
OL,13,Farrival warm milk every few hours to
OL,14,Fhelp it grow.
OL,16,FThe calf is only the second aardvark
OL,17,Fever born at the zoo in its 94-year
OL,18,Fhistory, making it a highly
OL,19,Fsignificant arrival.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
