FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1780304989
OL,3,CZookeepers step in to hand-rear
OL,4,Cnewborn aardvark 'Womble'
OL,6,FWhile the youngster was born healthy,
OL,7,Fits mother, Oni, was not producing
OL,8,Fenough milk to fully support her new
OL,9,Foffspring.
OL,11,FAardvarks are naturally nocturnal
OL,12,Fanimals so keepers had to provide
OL,13,Fsupplementary feeds throughout the
OL,14,Fnight for several weeks while Oni
OL,15,Fheaded off to forage for food.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1780304989
OL,3,CZookeepers step in to hand-rear
OL,4,Cnewborn aardvark 'Womble'
OL,6,FStaff have nicknamed the calf 'Womble'
OL,7,F- after the creatures from the
OL,8,Fchildren's novels and popular TV show
OL,9,F- because of long snout, wrinkly
OL,10,Fhairless skin, and enormous claws. The
OL,11,Fanimal's sex is still unknown.
OL,13,FZookeeper Sophie Tyson, who bottle-fed
OL,14,Fthe calf every few hours throughout
OL,15,Fthe night, praised the youngster's
OL,16,Fprogress.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1780304989
OL,3,CZookeepers step in to hand-rear
OL,4,Cnewborn aardvark 'Womble'
OL,6,FShe said: "For the first few weeks, we
OL,7,Fplaced the youngster into a cosy
OL,8,Fincubator each evening and it was
OL,9,Fbottle-fed warm milk every few hours
OL,10,Fthroughout the night before being
OL,11,Fcarefully reunited back with mum each
OL,12,Fmorning.
OL,14,F"Womble has gone from strength to
OL,15,Fstrength and is doing brilliantly, so
OL,16,Fnow lives full-time back with mum Oni
OL,17,F- and it's wonderful to see them
OL,18,Fsnuggled up side-by-side together."
OL,20,FWomble's birth is incredibly important
OL,21,Ffor international conservation efforts.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1780304989
OL,3,CZookeepers step in to hand-rear
OL,4,Cnewborn aardvark 'Womble'
OL,6,FThere are currently only 68 aardvarks
OL,7,Fin European zoos and just 114
OL,8,Fworldwide, making Chester Zoo one of
OL,9,Fonly a few organisations caring for
OL,10,Fthe species.
OL,12,FIn the wild, aardvarks are native to
OL,13,Fsub-Saharan Africa, where they face
OL,14,Fserious survival threats including
OL,15,Fhabitat loss caused by rapid
OL,16,Fagricultural development and hunting.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
